<li id="cite&#95;note-40"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="#cite_ref-40">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage" id="Wickens"><span class="ouvrage" id="Katie&#95;Wickens">Katie Wickens, <span class="noarchive">«&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.pcgamer.com/threads-threatens-to-muscle-in-on-mastodons-fediverse-and-admins-are-up-in-arms-about-it/"><cite style="font-style:normal;">Threads threatens to muscle in on Mastodon's Fediverse and admins are up in arms about it</cite></a>&#160;» [«&#160;Threads menace de fédérer avec le Fediverse de Mastodon et les administrateurs sont révoltés&#160;»] <small class="plainlinks cachelinks">&#91;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20231002182826/https://www.pcgamer.com/threads-threatens-to-muscle-in-on-mastodons-fediverse-and-admins-are-up-in-arms-about-it/">archive du <time class="nowrap" datetime="2023-10-02" data-sort-value="2023-10-02">2 octobre 2023</time></a>&#93;</small></span>, sur <span class="italique">PC Gamer</span> <small style="line-height:1em;">(consulté le <time class="nowrap" datetime="2024-03-22" data-sort-value="2024-03-22">22 mars 2024</time>)</small></span></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite&#95;note-41"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><a href="#cite_ref-41">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage" id="Barber"><span class="ouvrage" id="Gregory&#95;Barber"><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr> Gregory Barber, «&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.wired.com/story/metas-threads-could-make-or-break-the-fediverse/"><cite style="font-style:normal;" lang="en">Meta’s Threads Could Make—or Break—the Fediverse</cite></a>&#160;» [«&#160;Threads de Meta pourrait aider, ou briser, le Fediverse&#160;»], sur <span class="italique">Wired</span> <small style="line-height:1em;">(consulté le <time class="nowrap" datetime="2024-03-24" data-sort-value="2024-03-24">24 mars 2024</time>)</small></span></span></span>
